:"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""}},"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[8,278,53,90,65,204,114,102,351,353,385,25,63,118,215,19],"class_list":["post-2699","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-sin-al-ithm","tag-charity-al-sadaqah","tag-community-jamaah","tag-unlawful-al-haram","tag-justice-al-adl","tag-leadership-imamah","tag-major-sins-al-kabair","tag-manners-adab","tag-nation-ummah","tag-poor-al-miskin","tag-poverty-faqr","tag-reciprocity-al-tabadul","tag-rights-al-huquq","tag-rulers","tag-trials-al-balaa","tag-welfare-al-maslahah","tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-Hx","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34352,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/08\/04\/if-only-you-knew-poverty\/","url_meta":{"origin":2699,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Poverty: If only you knew reward for patience","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf only you knew the rewards you had with Allah, you would like to be increased in poverty and need.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 724 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/19\/ibn-masud-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":2699,"position":1},"title":"Abdullah on Qadr: Accept Allah\u2019s decree with patience or gratitude","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Qays ibn Khabtar reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAccept two things you dislike: death and poverty. By Allah, there is nothing but richness and poverty, and I do not care with which of them I am put to trial, for the right of Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37727,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/02\/23\/prophets-rejoice-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":2699,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Prophets rejoice at hardship, seeking reward","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most severely tested are the Prophets, and then the righteous. One of them would be tested with poverty until he could find nothing to cover himself but a cloak. One of them would rejoice\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/25\/prepare-for-poverty\/","url_meta":{"origin":2699,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faqr: Prepare for poverty if you love the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: He came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, I love the people of your house!\u201d The Prophet said to him, \u201cBy Allah? Then prepare to endure poverty, for poverty quickly approaches those who love us faster than a torrent flows\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/28\/prophet-suffers-with-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2699,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hunger: The Prophet suffers in poverty with his companions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Talhah reported: We complained about hunger to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and we lifted our garments to reveal stones tied to our stomachs, so the Messenger of Allah lifted his garment to reveal two stones. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2371 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38829,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/18\/dhikr-mawt-hope\/","url_meta":{"origin":2699,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Death: Remembering death balances hope in the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRemember often the destroyer of pleasures: death. Verily, no one living with plenty does so but that it diminishes his vain hopes, nor one living with little but that it increases his hope in Allah.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2699","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2699"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2699\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2699"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2699"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2699"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}